### What Just Happened?

You just created a real MongoDB (NoSQL) program! Here's what makes it work:

- This is the basic structure all MongoDB (NoSQL) programs follow
- The code you wrote is compiled/interpreted and executed
- The output appears in your terminal/console
- You can modify the message and run it again!

